dct_title_s: India topographical and Revenue Survey maps : on the scale one inch to one mile / published under the direction of Colonel H.I. Tuillier ; cartographers, J.E. Gastrell [and others].
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, form lines and spot heights. "Prepared for the use of the Survey Department of India and published under the authority of the Government of India." Title supplied by cataloguer. "Heliozincographed or Photozincographed at the Office of the Trigonometrical Branch, Survey of India, Dehra Dún."
